sections.heading: division No. 2; boundaries.Water division No
sections.text: 2 shall consist of (1) all lands that may be watered from the Loup, White, Niobrara, and Elkhorn Rivers and their tributaries and (2) all other lands of the state not included in any other water division.SourceLaws 1895, c. 69, ยง 3, p. 245;Laws 1911, c.
